text.tspan: Every shape is based on a 72x72 px grid and is built using
basic shapes. The serifs are 1 grid unit wide and
sometimes expand beyond the containing grid.
The shapes, paths and clipping were left live and it is
encouraged to take this font and make it your own. Edit it,
chop it up, make it cooler.
It is reccomended that you use this font as an svg,
hand-set the characters and export using Illustrator’s svg
